extends layouts/layout

block content
  h1 About Singh Auto
  p.muted Winnipeg’s trusted stop for oil, tires, brakes, and honest mechanic work.

  figure.service-hero
    img(src="/images/services/oil.jpg", alt="Singh Auto shop")

  h3 Our Story
  p
    | Singh Auto began with a simple goal: provide fast, transparent service without the usual dealer hassle.
    | From oil changes to brake jobs, we focus on quality workmanship and clear communication.

  h3 What We Stand For
  ul
    li Fair, upfront pricing with no surprise add-ons.
    li OEM-grade parts and proper torque specs on every job.
    li Friendly technicians who explain what your car actually needs.

  h3 Why Drivers Choose Us
  p.muted
    | Whether you’re here for a quick oil change or a full brake service, we treat your car like our own.
    | Most appointments are done the same day, with flexible evening and weekend availability.

  p
    a.btn(href="/book") Book an appointment